name: Haute-Loire
context: She received a letter asking whether she wanted to send some children to a very nice school in Haute-Loire at an elevation of one thousand meters.  She selected me and another boy. I'll be able to go there but she is afraid that perhaps I won't be safe there. Monday, January 4, 1943 Mr. Brémond came to La Rouvière today.I practically flooded him with tears.
